des:
Edison Smart products provide you a convenient and stress-free way to manage your home appliance. You can easily control our Edison products without the need to go to the switch, just let Alexa handle that for you.

[How to setup]
Please connect Alexa on your Amazon device (e.g. Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Echo spot etc.) to your Edison Smart product:
(1) Download our "Edison Smart" app from App Store(iOS) or Google play(Android). Register an Edison Smart account in the app (or login to the app if you already have an Edison Smart account);
(2) Configure the Edison Smart products you have in our Edison Smart app and assign appropriate place and name for your Edison Smart products for later use in the Edison Smart skill;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from iOS, android or Amazon App market;
(4) Configure your Amazon device with Alexa app;
(5) Open the skills category in the Alexa app and search "Edison Smart";
(6) Enable the "Edison Smart" skill and you will be navigated to the Edison Smart login page;
(7) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking.
You can enjoy voice control on your devices like:
"Alexa, turn on living room light."
"Alexa, turn off dining room light."
"Alexa, set kitchen light to 100%."
"Alexa, dim bedroom light to 30%."
If you setup groups in the app, you can even control multiple appliance at one time.
